creator: William Butler Yeats
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 13 recordings of A Deep-Sworn Vow by William Butler Yeats. This was the Weekly Poetry project for January 10, 2016. Read in Dutch by Algy Pug; Bruce Kachuk; Brian Darby; David Lawrence; Newgatenovelist; Greg Giordano; Ian King; Jennifer Fournier; Lee Ann Howlett; Leonard Wilson; Maria Kasper; Patrick Wallace and Winston Tharp. This is the weekly poem for the week of 10.01.2016. Have fun. ( Stav Nisser. ) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
